    "description": "<p><strong>SMP Global</strong> (hereinafter known as “SMP”), was incorporated in Singapore together with a team of knowledgeable, highly motivated, skillful multi-national mixture of Singaporean and German individuals.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We specialize end-to-end solutions on international forwarding, project heavy-lift operations, chartering of ALL kinds of vessel &amp; aircraft, customs brokerage and multi-modal transportation.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We offer a wide range of services such as, but not limited to others: covered warehousing, open yard storage, loading / unloading of containers, transportation planning, issuing of lifting plans, re-engineering, hydraulic lifting, machine refurbishment, trade services to various industries.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>SMP works closely with reputable and established companies in the Marine, Offshore, Oil &amp; Gas, Engineering and Construction with a wide scope from general cargoes to super oversize ones.</p>",
